birdfont (0.9) stable;

  * Color
  * Adjustable control point size
  * Select all path
  * Resize all selected paths
  * Import SVG files from Inkscape and Adobe Illustrator
  * Move control points with keyboard
  * Bugfixes
  * Join paths
  * German translation
  * Chinese translation

Coding for the release was done by Zhantong Zhang and Johan Mattsson. 
Translation was done by Zhantong Zhang, Robert Kabinger, Marc-Philipp 
Beuter and DiGro.

